{"tid":567162,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[Blacklist] 廟街食煲仔飯千奇唔好去生_海鮮菜館","createTime":"2018-02-20T15:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T18:51:55.000Z","uid":49285,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"048b655b74398537d7eed1725ee1e7b97903c042","tid":567162,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:16:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n收工約左朋友食飯 咁見耐無食就去左廟街食<br />\n某兩間比較出名既初四都無開 咁就求其揀左間叫生_既海鮮菜館食<br />\n結果就中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一入到去都中中地伏 餐牌痴立立 牆身又痴立立又多一粒粒黑色野痴住<br />\n都算啦都坐低左咪拿拿臨食完快d走<br />\n兩個人叫左個臘腸排骨煲仔飯 蠔餅 同腐乳椒絲通菜<br />\n等左15～20分鐘野食黎 煲仔飯我要排骨佢俾左雞 都算<br />\n咁就例牌落豉油再焗多佢兩分鐘 先發現煲仔飯底個碟有舊上手食剩既雞骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又落左豉油廢事叫佢換 反正都唔會成兜飯換俾你 咁照食啦<br />\n<br />\n之後到蠔餅 平時食既都係金金黃黃地色 佢就深啡色既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔熱又唔脆 都想像到d油係有幾黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食左兩啖無食<br />\n<br />\n個菜就平平 40蚊黎講質素算係咁<br />\n<br />\n但最仲要係食食下聽到天花板有聲 望上去個透明既假天花發現好多黑色污積<br />\n仲要見到有老鼠行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻起身埋單走<br />\n<br />\n各位千奇唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaf79e7b2ad24ee448d27216181c5d604c48780","tid":567162,"uid":44153,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n<br />\n收工約左朋友食飯 咁見耐無食就去左廟街食<br />\n某兩間比較出名既初四都無開 咁就求其揀左間叫生_既海鮮菜館食<br />\n結果就中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一入到去都中中地伏 餐牌痴立立 牆身又痴立立又多一粒粒黑色野痴住<br />\n都算啦都坐低左咪拿拿臨食完快d走<br />\n兩個人叫左個臘腸排骨煲仔飯 蠔餅 同腐乳椒絲通菜<br />\n等左15～20分鐘野食黎 煲仔飯我要排骨佢俾左雞 都算<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁就例牌落豉油再焗多佢兩分鐘 先發現煲仔飯底個碟有舊上手食剩既雞骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n我又落左豉油廢事叫佢換 反正都唔會成兜飯換俾你 咁照食啦<br />\n<br />\n之後到蠔餅 平時食既都係金金黃黃地色 佢就深啡色既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔熱又唔脆 都想像到d油係有幾黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食左兩啖無食<br />\n<br />\n個菜就平平 40蚊黎講質素算係咁<br />\n<br />\n但最仲要係食食下聽到天花板有聲 望上去個透明既假天花發現好多黑色污積<br />\n仲要見到有老鼠行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻起身埋單走<br />\n<br />\n各位千奇唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢PART都過到，最後竟然因為老鼠而走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a883663b94407a9fceb4ad343bf95351cd398aa9","tid":567162,"uid":49285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccaf79e7b2ad24ee448d27216181c5d604c48780","tid":567162,"uid":44153,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的<br />\n<br />\n收工約左朋友食飯 咁見耐無食就去左廟街食<br />\n某兩間比較出名既初四都無開 咁就求其揀左間叫生_既海鮮菜館食<br />\n結果就中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一入到去都中中地伏 餐牌痴立立 牆身又痴立立又多一粒粒黑色野痴住<br />\n都算啦都坐低左咪拿拿臨食完快d走<br />\n兩個人叫左個臘腸排骨煲仔飯 蠔餅 同腐乳椒絲通菜<br />\n等左15～20分鐘野食黎 煲仔飯我要排骨佢俾左雞 都算<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁就例牌落豉油再焗多佢兩分鐘 先發現煲仔飯底個碟有舊上手食剩既雞骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n我又落左豉油廢事叫佢換 反正都唔會成兜飯換俾你 咁照食啦<br />\n<br />\n之後到蠔餅 平時食既都係金金黃黃地色 佢就深啡色既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔熱又唔脆 都想像到d油係有幾黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食左兩啖無食<br />\n<br />\n個菜就平平 40蚊黎講質素算係咁<br />\n<br />\n但最仲要係食食下聽到天花板有聲 望上去個透明既假天花發現好多黑色污積<br />\n仲要見到有老鼠行過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻起身埋單走<br />\n<br />\n各位千奇唔好幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢PART都過到，最後竟然因為老鼠而走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"我已經落晒豉油撈埋兜飯 先見到舊雞骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋就算叫佢換我諗佢都唔會隻兜換 都係就咁換隻碟俾你就算<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係隻老鼠係exactly係我頭頂上面個透明既假天花<br />\n好驚佢突然間跌落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613676ca740d34495135c129bf665bfd657c18b4","tid":567162,"uid":108946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:21:09.000Z","msg":"你都算忍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4786ea1cbae6370a6f67948b42d812774d773e","tid":567162,"uid":23716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"圖都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d545266cde8d779d37c7c0e9495ad9e22b702da7","tid":567